title: Sticky Chutney Beef Strips with Roasted Veggies & Smokey Aioli
description: Here’s a hearty beef bowl that draws inspiration from countless cuisines and brings it straight to your plate. Herby beef strips,
coated in a sweet chutney meets roasted veggies tossed with greens, and there’s a dollop of smokey aioli to finish it off.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
